<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ro">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Abonează-te</title>
  <style>
      body{
          font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
          text-align: center;
          margin: 50px;
          background-color: #f0f0f0;
          color: #333;
          display: flex;
          justify-content: center;
          align-items: flex-start;
          height: 100vh;
          padding: 50px;
      }

      .container{
          max-width: 80%;
          padding: 20px;
          border-radius: 10px;
          background: linear-gradient(134deg, #1e3a8a, #4f46e5);
          color: white;
          box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
          display: flex;
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: center;
      }

      input{
          width: 80%;
          padding: 10px;
          margin: 5px 0;
          border: 1px solid #ccc;
          background-color: #f8f9fa;
          color: #000;
      }

      button{
          background-color: #1e3a8a;
          color: white;
          padding: 10px 15px;
          border: none;
          border-radius: 5px;
          cursor: pointer;
          font-weight: bold;
          transition: background 0.3s ease-in-out;
          margin-top: 10px;
          width: 100%;
      }

      button:hover{
          background-color: #4f46e5;
      }

      button:active{
          background-color: yellow;
          color: black;
      }

      #message{
          color: #e2e8f0;
          display: none;
          font-weight: bold;
          margin-top: 10px;
      }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
     <div class="container">
         <h2>Bun venit!</h2>
         <p>Alătură-te paginii noastre pentru a fi la curent cu cele mai noi date.</p>
         <form id="subscribe-form">
             <input type="email" id="email" placeholder="Introdu adresa de email" required>
             <button type="submit">Abonează-te</button>
         </form>
         <p id="message">Te-ai abonat cu succes!</p>
     </div>
   
<script>
    document.getElementById("subscribe-form").addEventListener("submit", function(event){
        event.preventDefault();
        document.getElementById("message").style.display = "block";
    });

</script>


</body>
</html>
